_sText:
This is a magical and mysterious medieval map that takes place in modern day where Terrorists try to blow up the old ruins of the town because of their religious beliefs! Counter Terrorists own the castle and are ready to fight!

This map does have some creepy sections so be aware!
Be curious to see what that blood trail is leading to, see where you may start up at, you may not even start at the usual spawn!
Comment me to see how I can improve the map in later updates!
Have fun!.
